## Input

```css
@page :left {
  $padding: 12px !default;
  $scale: 1 + 2 * 3;
  padding: $padding * $scale;
  font: {
    size: 12px;
    family: $font-stack;
  }
  $map: (
    ($padding + 1): foo,
    (1 + 2): bar,
  );

  @top-left {
    $margin: 4px !global;
    margin: ($margin + 2) / 2;
    border: 1px solid $color {
      width: 1px;
      color: $color;
    }
  }

  @top-right {
    theme.$gutter: 8px;
    padding: theme.$gutter;
  }
}

```


